data.description: Just around the bend from picturesque Norris Lake, this open concept, 3-bedroom 2 full bath single family home is ready for a great family!! With a bright open floor plan and a large kitchen set in the center of this beautiful home, there is plenty of room for a growing family. With neutral tones in the main living space, granite counter tops and a luxurious soaking tub to enjoy, there's not a whole lot to do on this home. A nice yard for entertainment and a large front and back porch offer more than enough space to sit outside and enjoy the sights and sounds of nature. And with Norris Lake just steps away, there is plenty of space for boat parking too. Call for details today. Buyer to verify all information
